Yes. In fact, **I recommend multiple prompts**. One giant prompt usually produces a lower-quality result because the AI tries to cover everything at once. Breaking it into phases is closer to how a real software architect works.

Given your goal, I would create a **Project Master Guide** consisting of multiple prompts. Together, they'll become the complete blueprint for the project.

